E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('995','6','春风','中国嘉鱼网','<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">11</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">25</span>至<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">26</span>日，国家发改委社会发展司袁B、省发改委社会发展处处长李革鹏、市发改委副主任熊国良一行来嘉鱼，就我县文化旅游产业及经济发展情况进行了专题调研。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">袁</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">B</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">一行听取了嘉鱼县&ldquo;十二五&rdquo;规划、文化旅游资源发展状况、产业发展规划等方面的汇报，并先后到山湖温泉休闲度假区、三湖连江风景区、官桥村低丘岗地改造现场、新农村整村推进项目建设现场、官桥八组生态文化风景区进行了实地调研，对嘉鱼县文化旅游产业的发展空间和资源优势给予充分肯定，并对我县确立的&ldquo;两城两区&rdquo;、&ldquo;两圈两带&rdquo;，打造湖北经济强县，长江临港新城的目标寄予厚望。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">县发改局局长顾兴茂、文体新局局长刘焰才、官桥镇镇长朱明凤等陪同调研。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd;