-top: windowtext 0.5pt solid; border-right: windowtext 0.5pt solid\"><span style=\"font-size: small\"><font face=\"宋体\">张小芸 15926935858</font></span></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr height=\"30\" style=\"height: 22.5pt; mso-height-source: userset\">\r\n            <td class=\"xl24\" height=\"30\" style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 0.5pt solid; text-align: center; border-left: windowtext 0.5pt solid; background-color: transparent; border-top-color: windowtext; height: 22.5pt; border-right: windowtext 0.5pt solid\">\r\n            <p><span style=\"font-size: small\"><font face=\"宋体\">服务内容概述</font></span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td class=\"xl24\" colspan=\"8\" style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 0.5pt solid; text-align: center; background-color: transparent; border-left-color: windowtext; border-top: windowtext 0.5pt solid; border-right: windowtext 0.5pt solid\"><span style=\"font-size: small\"><font face=\"宋体\">拆除或闲置污染防治设施审批</font></span></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr height=\"83\" style=\"height: 62.25pt; mso-height-source: userset\">\r\n            <td class=\"xl24\" height=\"83\" style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 0.5pt solid; text-align: center; border-left: windowtext 0.5pt solid; background-color: transparent; border-top-color: windowtext; height: 62.25pt; border-right: windowtext 0.5pt solid\">\r\n            <p><span style=\"font-size: small\"><font face=\"宋体\">政策法规依据</font></span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td class=\"xl25\" width=\"527\" colspan=\"8\" style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 0.5pt solid; text-align: left; background-color: transparent; width: 395pt; border-left-color: windowtext; border-top: windowtext 0.5pt solid; border-right: black 0.5pt solid\">\r\n            <p><span style=\"font-size: small\"><font face=\"宋体\">《中华人民共和国环境保护法》第二十六条</font></span></p>\r\n            <p><span style=\"font-size: small\"><font face=\"宋体\">《中华人民共和国大气污染防治法》第十二条</font></span></p>\r\n            <p><span style=\"font-size: small\"><font face=\"宋体\">《中华人民共和国水污染防治法》第十四条 </font></span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr height=\"78\" style=\"height: 58.5pt; mso-height-source: userset\">\r\n            <td class=\"xl24\" height=\"78\" style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 0.5pt solid; text-align: center; border-left: windowtext 0.5pt solid; background-color: transparent; border-top-color: windowtext; height: 58.5pt; border-right: windowtext 0.5pt solid\">\r\n            <p><span style=\"font-size: small\"><font face=\"宋体\">事项申办条件</font></span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td class=\"xl25\" width=\"527\" colspan=\"8\" style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 0.5pt solid; text-align: left; background-color: transparent; width: 395pt; border-left-color: windowtext; border-top: windowtext 0.5pt solid; border-right: black 0.5pt solid\">\r\n            <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n            <p><span style=\"font-size: small\"><font face=\"宋体\">企业需拆除或闲置污染治理设施的（须提前向环保部门申报，设施故障被迫停运必须当时报停，次日补办报停手续）。关闭、闲置、拆除污染防治设施后，其污染物通过其他设施治理可以达到排放标准的，才能关闭、闲置、拆除。<br />\r\n            </font></span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr height=\"170\" style=\"height: 127.5pt; mso-height-source: userset\">\r\n            <td class=\"xl24\" height=\"170\" style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 0.5pt solid; text-align: center; border-left: windowtext 0.5pt solid; background-color: transparent; border-top-color: windowtext; height: 127.5pt; border-right: windowtext 0.5pt solid\"><span style=\"font-size: small\"><font face=\"宋体\">申报材料</font></span></td>\r\n            <td class=\"xl25\" width=\"527\" colspan=\"8\" style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 0.5pt solid; text-align: left; background-color: transparent; width: 395pt; border-left-color: windowtext; border-top: windowtext 0.5pt solid; border-right: black 0.5pt solid\"><span style=\"font-size: small\"><font face=\"宋体\">1、排污单位申请拆除或闲置污染治理设施的报告（原件4份）；<br />\r\n            2、工商局提供的停业、转产证明及其他特殊情况证明；<br />\r\n            3、污染防治设施的基本情况和运行情况报告（原件4份）；<br />\r\n            4、拆除或闲置污染防治设施后排放污染物达标的保证或补救措施的说明材料（原件4份）；<br />\r\n            5、污染防治设施重新安装、使用的时间的说明材料（原件4份）；<br />\r\n            6、申请前一季度的生产记录复印件及环境监测报告<br />\r\n            7、《污染防治设施拆除或闲置申请表》（原件4份）；</font></span></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr height=\"76\" style=\"height: 57pt; mso-height-source: userset\">\r\n            <td class=\"xl24\" height=\"76\" style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 0.5pt solid; text-align: center; border-left: windowtext 0.5pt solid; background-color: transparent; border-top-color: windowtext; height: 57pt; border-right: windowtext 0.5pt solid\">\r\n            <p><span style=\"font-size: small\"><font face=\"宋体\">办理处理流程</font></span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td class=\"xl28\" width=\"527\" colspan=\"8\" style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 0.5pt solid; text-align: left; background-color: transparent; width: 395pt; border-left-color: windowtext; border-top: windowtext 0.5pt solid; border-right: windowtext 0.5pt solid\"><span style=\"font-size: small\"><font face=\"宋体\">县行政服务中心环保窗口申请&mdash;&mdash;受理&mdash;&mdash;县环保局行政许可科审查&mdash;&mdash;县环保局决定&mdash;&mdash;窗口送达许可决定</font></span></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr height=\"52\" style=\"height: 39pt; mso-height-source: userset\">\r\n            <td class=\"xl24\" height=\"52\" style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 0.5pt solid; text-align: center; border-left: windowtext 0.5pt solid; background-color: transparent; border-top-color: windowtext; height: 39pt; border-right: windowtext 0.5pt solid\">\r\n            <p><span style=\"font-size: small\"><font face=\"宋体\">服务办理时限</font></span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td class=\"xl28\" width=\"527\" colspan=\"8\" style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 0.5pt solid; text-align: center; background-color: transparent; width: 395pt; border-left-color: windowtext; border-top: windowtext 0.5pt solid; border-right: windowtext 0.5pt solid\"><span style=\"font-size: small\"><font face=\"宋体\">自受理申请之日起20个工作日内</font></span></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr height=\"47\" style=\"height: 35.25pt; mso-height-source: userset\">\r\n            <td class=\"xl24\" height=\"47\" style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 0.5pt solid; text-align: center; border-left: windowtext 0.5pt solid; background-color: transparent; border-top-color: windowtext; height: 35.25pt; border-right: windowtext 0.5pt solid\"><span style=\"font-size: small\"><font face=\"宋体\">收费标准</font></span></td>\r\n            <td class=\"xl28\" width=\"527\" colspan=\"8\" style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 0.5pt solid; text-align: center; background-color: transparent; width: 395pt; border-left-color: windowtext; border-top: windowtext 0.5pt solid; border-right: windowtext 0.5pt solid\"><span style=\"font-size: small\"><font face=\"宋体\">不收费</font></span></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr height=\"46\" style=\"height: 34.5pt; mso-height-source: userset\">\r\n            <td class=\"xl24\" height=\"46\" style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 0.5pt solid; text-align: center; border-left: windowtext 0.5pt solid; background-color: transparent; border-top-color: windowtext; height: 34.5pt; border-right: windowtext 0.5pt solid\"><span style=\"font-size: small\"><font face=\"宋体\">表格下载</font></span></td>\r\n            <td class=\"xl28\" width=\"527\" colspan=\"8\" style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 0.5pt solid; background-color: transparent; width: 395pt; border-left-color: windowtext; border-top: windowtext 0.5pt solid; border-right: windowtext 0.5pt solid\">\r\n            <p style=\"text-align: center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n            <span style=\"font-size: small\">\r\n            <p style=\"text-align: center\"><font face=\"宋体\">　 </font></p>\r\n            </span><font size=\"2\" face=\"宋体\">\r\n            <div style=\"padding-bottom: 6px; padding-left: 6px; padding-right: 6px; padding-top: 6px\"><fieldset><legend><span style=\"font-size: small\">污染防治设施闲置或拆除申请表</span></legend>\r\n            <table border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n                <tbody>\r\n                    <tr>\r\n                        <td><span style=\"font-size: small\"><img border=\"0\" alt=\"文件类型: .doc\" style=\"vertical-align: baseline\" src=\"/e/data/images/downfile.jpg\" /></span></td>\r\n                        <td><a title=\"污染防治设施闲置或拆除申请表\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"/d/file/jiayuxianxingzhengxukemulu/huanbaoju/2011-10-26/8b67ec3c92d13edf9cc9aa00cee9cb98.doc\"><span style=\"font-size: small\">8b67ec3c92d13edf9cc9aa00cee9cb98.doc</span></a><span style=\"font-size: small\">&nbsp;(28.50 KB)</span></td>\r\n                    </tr>\r\n                </tbody>\r\n            </table>\r\n            </fieldset></div>\r\n            </font></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr height=\"58\" style=\"height: 43.5pt; mso-height-source: userset\">\r\n            <td class=\"xl24\" height=\"58\" style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 0.5pt solid; text-align: center; border-left: windowtext 0.5pt solid; background-color: transparent; border-top-color: windowtext; height: 43.5pt; border-right: windowtext 0.5pt solid\"><span style=\"font-size: small\"><font face=\"宋体\">备注</font></span></td>\r\n            <td class=\"xl28\" width=\"527\" colspan=\"8\" style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 0.5pt solid; text-align: center; background-color: transparent; width: 395pt; border-left-color: windowtext; border-top: windowtext 0.5pt solid; border-right: windowtext 0.5pt solid\"><span style=\"font-size: small\"><font face=\"宋体\">　</font></span></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"font-size: small\">&nbsp;</span></p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1053','6','周艳','中国嘉鱼网','<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">12</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">月</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">6</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">日下午，嘉鱼县召开四大家扩大会议，通报我县当前集中开展的&ldquo;两违&rdquo;建筑整治情况，安排部署下阶段控违拆违工作。熊征宇、余珂、李国光、李鹏谋、葛婷等在家的县四大家领导出席会议。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">县委书记熊征宇主持会议并讲话。他说，连日来，我县集中开展了一场&ldquo;两违&rdquo;建筑整治行动，力度大、声势大、影响大，全县上下思想行动高度统一，各镇各部门大力支持配合，整治行动效果明显，得到上级党委政府高度理解和支持，受到广大干部群众及社会各界的一致拥护和赞许。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">熊征宇要求，下一阶段，全县上下要坚定信心、坚定不移、乘势而上打好控违拆违这场硬仗。在整治行动中，要讲究策略、讲究方法，强力推进、稳步实施，坚持原则、把握界限，多管齐下、各个击破，掌握情报、做好预案，打击少数、教育多数。要在全面推进、纵深推进拆违防控工作的同时，实施好保障性住房建设工程，切实保证广大群众住有所居。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; word-break: break-all; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">熊征宇强调，控违拆违是发展大势逼着干的事，是广大人民群众要求干的事，是法律法规明确规定必须干的事，理应树立维护大局、维护稳定的观念，举全县之力，思想认识高度统一，成立工作专班，落实包保责任，严明纪律、严肃法纪，</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\">全力以赴</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">打好整治&ldquo;两违&rdquo;建筑的持久战、攻坚战，</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\">为我县建设湖北经济强县、长江临港新城作出应有的贡献。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">会议听取了我县近期&ldquo;两违&rdquo;工作整治情况。截至目前，我县共出动重型机械</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">4</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">台，执法车辆</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">60</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">余台，执法人员</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">300</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">余人，拆除违法违章建筑</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">55</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">处，拆违面积</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">3.6</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">万平方米。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">各镇、各职能部门主要负责人参加会议。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1054','6','李发扬、汪姝琴','咸宁日报','<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">&ldquo;以转变作风促发展，将<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&lsquo;</span>治庸问责<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&rsquo;</span>工作办成群众满意工程和干部满意工程。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&rdquo;11</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">30</span>日，嘉鱼县<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&ldquo;</span>治庸问责<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&rdquo;</span>动员大会提出，把治庸问责工作作为改进干部作风、提升服务效能、优化发展环境的突破口。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\">11</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\">月，县委组建了四个调研组，就目前党员干部作风、行政审批服务、企业协调服务、城市建设管理等不同侧面，进行了专题调研，发现的问题主要表现在：党员干部中存在<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&ldquo;</span>四庸、四懒、四散、四软<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&rdquo;</span>问题，直接或间接地损害了嘉鱼形象，耽误了嘉鱼的发展。具体体现在工作执行力不强，行政审批效率不高，一些重点工作推进力度不大，少数部门服务企业发展意识不够浓厚等。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">该县首先从会风问责抓起。当天，该县对开会迟到和<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&ldquo;</span>开小差<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&rdquo;</span>的人员进行摄影摄像，对无故不参会的人员会后立即启动问责程序，对<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">22</span>名干部进行了通报批评。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">同时，该县还全面启动了县委县政府重大决策执行情况和重点项目推进情况问责工作。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">县委、政府决策的重大事项，通过全面清查会议纪要，对没有落实的向相关责任人发出问责通知书，责其说明情况，并区别情况采取相应追责措施。当前一段时间，该县还把违法用地、违规建设整治工作中失职渎职人员作为问责的重点对象。凡查出工作中不落实的，第一次通报批评，第二次诫勉谈话，第三次就地免职。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\">治庸问责<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&rdquo;</span>工作是一项长期性、系统性工程。该县进一步健全长效机制，以制度管人，如对年终目标责任制考核办法进行改革，明确提出，县里的重点项目、重大决策事项落实情况将作为目标考核的重要内容，大幅度提高其分值比重。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">通过<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&ldquo;</span>敢治敢问、严治严问、善治善问、常治常问<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&rdquo;</span>，该县力争达到转作风、促发展的效果，让<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">群众享受到干部服务效能提升的实惠；同时让干部受到教育、提升能力，形成凭实绩论英雄，凭能力用干部，<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&ldquo;</span>能者上，庸者下<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&rdquo;</span>的用人机制和导向，让干事者有舞台，干成事者有地位，也真正让干部满意。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1055','6','黄俊鹏、费保康 ','中国嘉鱼网','<p><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 为了维护长江干线武汉区段水上通航环境和通航秩序，更加方便船舶航行，保障船舶、设施和人命、财产安全，防止船舶污染水域，武汉海事局决定自<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2011</span>年<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">12</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">7</span>日零时起在长江干线武汉区段实施电子巡航检查。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">实施水域上界自长江航道左岸胡家洲（中游航道里程<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">165.0km</span>）与右岸小清江河（中游航道里程<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">165.0km</span>）的连线，下界至长江航道左岸涨渡湖口闸下（下游航道里程<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">984.0km</span>）与右岸泥矶过河标（下游航道里程<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">984.0km</span>）的连线之间的长江干线<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">224.5km</span>通航水域。主要内容是监督船舶航行、停泊和作业秩序；纠正船舶违法行为，必要时使用海事执法船（车）登船检查、制止船舶违法行为，依法实施海事行政处罚或网上协查；发布限航、禁航等航行通（警）告及安全航行预警信息，提供气象、水文等安全信息咨询服务。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">海事部门要求各有船单位、船舶应自觉遵守有关航行、停泊和作业规定，按规定安装使用<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">AIS</span>（船舶自动识别系统）、<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">GPS</span>（全球定位系统）等信息化设备，配合海事管理机构的现场安全监管，共建&ldquo;畅通、高效、安全、绿色&rdquo;的内河航运。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1056','156','','嘉鱼政务网','<p><span style=\\\\\"font-size: medium\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp; 请婚姻当事人前往省民政厅办理相关手续，具体流程可咨询县民政局。电话：0715-6353788。</span></span></p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1057','6','熊铁山','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2011-12-07/1ad91dc8d6a26dbed69382dbf5487f7b.jpg\\\\\" /></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><br />\r\n<span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px\\\\\">培训班现场<br />\r\n</span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: left\\\\\">\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">12</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">7</span>日，全省乡镇党委书记轮训班在我县官桥八组举办，来自全省各县、市、区的<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">200</span>多名乡镇党委书记参加了培训。副省长赵斌，省委组织部副部长陈绪群，咸宁市委书记黄楚平，嘉鱼县委书记熊征宇出席开班仪式。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">赵斌指出，有针对性地开展科学发展主题培训，加强乡镇党委书记队伍建设是实现湖北跨越式发展的基础工程，是夯实基层基础的现实需要，更是建设高素质基层干部队伍的迫切需要。乡镇党委书记要&ldquo;围绕四个建设，提高四种能力&rdquo;：围绕社会主义新农村建设，提高推动发展的能力，着力加快农业产业化、农村城镇化和工业化步伐；围绕和谐社会建设，提高维护稳定的能力，承担维稳责任，依靠群众维稳，依法行政；围绕服务型政府建设，提高改善民生的能力，积极推进政府职能转变，推动强农惠农政策全面落实，促进民生工程顺利实施；围绕加强基层党组织建设，提高抓班子、带队伍的能力，建强乡镇领导班子，激发基层党员干部的活力。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">赵斌希望全体学员珍惜这次培训的机会，认真学习，加强交流，共同提高，学以致用，为促进本地经济社会跨越发展、群众生活水平不断提高作出更大的贡献。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">黄楚平代表市委、市政府对全省乡镇党委书记轮训班在我县官桥八组举办表示了热烈欢迎，并就咸宁市近年来的经济社会发展情况向学员们作了介绍。黄楚平表示，将认真学习借鉴兄弟市的先进经验，取长补短，开拓创新。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">省委组织部副部长陈绪群主持开班仪式。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">据悉，本次乡镇党委书记轮训班设有分组讨论、专题报告、案例教学、现场参观等课程，并特邀省委党校、省社科院等单位的专家、教授为学员们进行专题讲座。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2011-12-07/a6ab6e274182ced48f847f9474a05279.jpg\\\\\" /></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">培训班现场</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1058','6','张姝','中国嘉鱼网','<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2011-12-07/56950deca6ecd701ab805817e0d9e7ec.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">黄楚平一行在中能锂电调研</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">12</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">月</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">7</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">日，市委书记黄楚平，市委常委、市委秘书长黄剑雄一行赴嘉鱼县考察调研。县委书记熊征宇，县委副书记、县长余珂等县四大家领导陪同调研。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">黄楚平对我县今年以来取得的工作成绩表示肯定，他说，嘉鱼县的工业增加值、地方一般预算收入、农民人均纯收入增幅等多项指标在全市居领先地位，取得了可喜的发展局面，为全市的经济社会发展作出了重要贡献；嘉鱼新一届县委领导班子充满朝气，有很好的精神状态，对未来五年的发展规划思路清晰，目标明确。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">黄楚平说，嘉鱼的发展迎来了大有可为的关键时期，要抢抓机遇、趁势而上，按照全县党代会上提出的目标层层抓落实。他要求，嘉鱼要围绕建设经济强县下功夫，抓大产业、大项目、建大园区；要围绕建设临港新城下功夫，利用长江岸线优势，发展沿江产业链；要围绕建设旅游胜地下功夫，进一步挖掘自然、人文资源，把旅游业做大做强；要围绕建设鱼米之乡下功夫，调整产业结构，加快发展观光农业、生态农业；要围绕建设幸福嘉鱼下功夫，着力办实事、惠民生，提高群众的幸福指数。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">熊征宇汇报了我县经济社会发展情况。他说，今年以来，我县着力打基础、管长远，坚持一区多园兴工业、优化结构强农业、科学开发活旅游、加大投入固基础、多办实事惠民生，全县经济社会实现了又好又快发展。预计全年可完成生产总值</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">108</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">亿元，同比增长</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">17%</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">；规模工业增加值</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">64</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">亿元，增长</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">25.8%</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">熊征宇说，</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2012</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">年我县将继续推动工业发展迈大步，确保农业和第三产业发展上水平，在城乡建设、交通建设和社会事业发展上取得新突破。围绕既定目标，将着力实施工业倍增、农业转型、旅游跨越、城市宜居、交通畅通、和谐惠民六大工程建设，为早日把嘉鱼建成湖北经济强县、长江临港新城打下坚实基础。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">会前，黄楚平一行参观考察了县经济开发区内峰华科技有限公司、中能锂电科技有限公司等地。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2011-12-07/a2bac0fb33c0818172afa30a6beb4b41.jpg\\\\\" /></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">调研会现场</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1059','6','熊铁山','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2011-12-07/3b80ad46e222832588983a5e500e7bc9.jpg\\\\\" /></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><br />\r\n<span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px\\\\\">参观农田水利建设现场<br />\r\n</span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;<span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">12</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">7</span>日，副省长赵斌一行在市委书记黄楚平及县领导熊征宇、余珂、熊武华、魏萍等陪同下，深入嘉鱼县官桥镇调研农田水利建设和现代农业发展。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: left\\\\\">\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\">在该镇朱砂村七组聂家海塘堰整治现场，</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">赵斌详细了解了施工的进度及竣工后所带来的效益。</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\">他指出，农田水利基本建设是农村工作的重点，各级各部门要把农田水利基本建设工作摆在农村工作的突出位置，务必统筹规划，扎实推进。要加快农村饮水安全、农业灌溉配套、病险水库除险加固等工程建设，进一步明确重点，细化任务，强化措施，真抓实干，确保农村水利改革发展各项工作落到实处，取得实效。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">在湖北大禾现代设施农业调研时，赵斌指出，农业要发展，农民要增收，就必须要调整农村产业结构，改变落后的小农经济现状；要注重产品品质，实施精细化管理，提高产品的内在竞争力；大力发展特色农业，加快发展现代农业。<span lang=\\\\\"E