e=\\\\\"font-size: medium\\\\\">\r\n            <p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"center\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n            <p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"center\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\">申</span></p>\r\n            </span>\r\n            <p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"center\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 15pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n            <p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"center\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: medium\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\">报</span></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 15pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n            <p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"center\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: medium\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\">材</span></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 15pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n            <p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"center\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: medium\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\">料</span></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 15pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width=\\\\\"421\\\\\" style=\\\\\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; border-left: #ece9d8; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 5.4pt; width: 315.85pt; padding-right: 5.4